    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is firm and supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since purchase. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized intervals. The engine bay is detailed and pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or weather exposure. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy. Included are all original keys, the window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of all service records.",
